title: Hilulim Kosher Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Moroccan, Kosher, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Middle Eastern, Moroccan, and vegetarian kosher food. Large selection of vegan suitable salads and sides plus has falafel and a vegetarian soup of the day. Vegans should ask if your salad dressing contains mayo or honey.
